Class ServerConnectorBootstrap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wso2.transport.http.netty.listener.ServerConnectorBootstrap

  • public class ServerConnectorBootstrap
extends Object
    ServerConnectorBootstrap is the heart of the HTTP Server Connector.

    This is responsible for creating the serverBootstrap and allow bind/unbind to interfaces
